QuestData.Title: The Jailer's Gauntlet
QuestData.Description:
Maw Walker! I have been looking for you.
Word is there is a new gathering of the Jailer's forces in Torghast. I'm not sure what they are doing, but it can't be good.
Perhaps you should put an end to their plans?
QuestData.LogDescription: Enter the new portal in the Torghast Lobby.

Objectives.Objective: Enter the new portal in the Torghast Lobby.
